{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775867342671,"sessionID":"ses_2860fd53cffeIZwy9rcWI6qt9T","part":{"id":"prt_d79f12f28001dMBT6SdLb4TG9v","messageID":"msg_d79f1277f001ZQrRJSi0TRE57G","sessionID":"ses_2860fd53cffeIZwy9rcWI6qt9T","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-63c68bb33ae84864908191dda64609c5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-021: CLI build 命令\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: 实现 AgentCube CLI 的 `build` 命令，用于从打包好的工作空间构建容器镜像。该命令支持本地 Docker 构建和云端构建两种模式，能够自动管理版本号、验证构建前置条件，并集成 Docker 服务进行镜像构建。\n6: \n7: ## Purpose\n8: \n9: 提供 `kubectl-agentcube build` 命令，实现：\n10: \n11: 1. **本地 Docker 构建**：使用本地 Docker 守护进程构建容器镜像\n12: 2. **云端构建**：集成云服务商（如华为云）的构建服务\n13: 3. **版本管理**：自动递增版本号（patch 级别），构建失败时回滚版本\n14: 4. **代理支持**：支持自定义代理 URL 进行依赖解析\n15: 5. **构建结果输出**：输出镜像名称、ID、大小等构建信息\n16: 6. **元数据更新**：更新 `agent_metadata.yaml` 中的构建信息\n17: \n18: ## Module\n19: \n20: `cmd/cli` - AgentCube CLI 工具包\n21: \n22: ## Language\n23: \n24: Python 3.10+\n25: \n26: ## Size\n27: \n28: M\n29: \n30: ## Scope\n31: \n32: ### In Scope\n33: \n34: 1. **BuildRuntime 类实现** (`agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py`)\n35:    - `build()` 主方法，支持本地和云端构建模式\n36:    - `_increment_version()` - 版本号递增逻辑\n37:    - `_validate_build_prerequisites()` - 构建前置条件验证\n38:    - `_build_local()` - 本地 Docker 构建\n39:    - `_build_cloud()` - 云端构建（华为云等）\n40:    - `_update_build_metadata()` - 更新构建元数据\n41: \n42: 2. **CLI 命令集成** (`agentcube/cli/main.py`)\n43:    - `build()` Typer 命令函数\n44:    - 命令行参数：`--workspace`, `--proxy`, `--cloud-provider`, `--output`, `--verbose`\n45:    - 错误处理和用户反馈\n46: \n47: 3. **Docker 服务集成** (`agentcube/services/docker_service.py`)\n48:    - `build_image()` - 构建镜像方法\n49:    - 支持构建参数（buildargs）\n50:    - 支持代理配置\n51:    - 返回镜像信息（名称、ID、大小、构建时间）\n52: \n53: 4. **元数据服务集成** (`agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`)\n54:    - 加载和保存 `agent_metadata.yaml`\n55:    - 版本管理\n56:    - 构建结果持久化\n57: \n58: ### Out of Scope\n59: \n60: - Docker 守护进程安装和配置\n61: - 云服务提供商 SDK 实现（使用已有 SDK）\n62: - Dockerfile 生成（由 `pack` 命令完成）\n63: - 镜像推送功能（由 `publish` 命令完成）\n64: \n65: ## Impact Analysis\n66: \n67: ### Components Impacted\n68: \n69: 1. **CLI 工具包** (`cmd/cli`)\n70:    - 添加 `build` 命令到 Typer 应用\n71:    - 新增 `BuildRuntime` 类\n72:    - 更新导入和依赖\n73: \n74: 2. **Docker 服务** (`agentcube/services/docker_service.py`)\n75:    - 确保已实现 `build_image()` 方法\n76:    - 支持代理配置\n77:    - 支持构建参数传递\n78: \n79: 3. **元数据服务** (`agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`)\n80:    - 需要支持版本更新\n81:    - 需要支持构建信息存储\n82: \n83: 4. **用户工作流**\n84:    - `pack` → `build` → `publish` 的完整链路\n85:    - 元数据文件在命令间传递状态\n86: \n87: ### Dependencies\n88: \n89: **核心依赖**（已在 `pyproject.toml` 中定义）：\n90: - `typer[all]>=0.9.0` - CLI 框架\n91: - `pydantic>=2.0.0` - 数据验证\n92: - `pyyaml>=6.0` - YAML 解析\n93: - `docker>=6.0.0` - Docker SDK\n94: - `rich>=13.0.0` - 美化输出\n95: - `semver>=3.0.0` - 语义化版本管理\n96: \n97: **可选依赖**：\n98: - `httpx>=0.24.0` - HTTP 客户端（云端构建）\n99: \n100: ### Security Considerations\n101: \n102: 1. **Docker 守护进程访问**\n103:    - 验证 Docker 守护进程是否可访问\n104:    - 检查 Docker 权限\n105:    - 避免构建敏感信息泄露到镜像\n106: \n107: 2. **代理安全**\n108:    - 支持安全的代理 URL（HTTPS）\n109:    - 避免在日志中输出代理凭证\n110:    - 支持代理认证（环境变量）\n111: \n112: 3. **元数据安全**\n113:    - 避免在元数据中存储敏感信息\n114:    - 版本号递增时的原子性\n115:    - 构建失败时的回滚机制\n116: \n117: 4. **云构建安全**\n118:    - 支持云服务认证凭证\n119:    - 避免在日志中输出凭证\n120:    - 支持凭证轮换\n121: \n122: ## Design Decisions\n123: \n124: ### 构建模式选择\n125: \n126: **选择**：支持本地和云端两种构建模式\n127: \n128: **理由**：\n129: - 本地构建：开发、测试、小规模部署\n130: - 云端构建：生产环境、大规模部署、CI/CD\n131: - 满足不同用户需求\n132: \n133: **实现**：\n134: ```python\n135: if build_mode == \"local\":\n136:     return self._build_local(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n137: elif build_mode == \"cloud\":\n138:     return self._build_cloud(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n139: else:\n140:     raise ValueError(f\"Unsupported build mode: {build_mode}\")\n141: ```\n142: \n143: ### 版本管理策略\n144: \n145: **选择**：自动递增 patch 版本，构建失败时回滚\n146: \n147: **理由**：\n148: - 自动版本号管理减少用户负担\n149: - 构建失败时保持版本一致性\n150: - 符合语义化版本规范\n151: \n152: **实现**：\n153: ```python\n154: def _increment_version(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata) -> Any:\n155:     original_version = metadata.version\n156:     # 递增版本号\n157:     new_version = semver.VersionInfo.parse(original_version).bump_patch()\n158:     metadata.version = str(new_version)\n159:     # 更新元数据文件\n160:     self.metadata_service.save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)\n161:     return original_version  # 返回原始版本以便回滚\n162: ```\n163: \n164: ### 代理配置策略\n165: \n166: **选择**：通过 `--proxy` 参数传递代理 URL，传递给 Docker 构建参数\n167: \n168: **理由**：\n169: - 支持企业内网环境\n170: - 灵活配置代理\n171: - 避免硬编码\n172: \n173: **实现**：\n174: ```python\n175: build_args = {}\n176: if proxy:\n177:     build_args[\"HTTP_PROXY\"] = proxy\n178:     build_args[\"HTTPS_PROXY\"] = proxy\n179: ```\n180: \n181: ### 输出格式策略\n182: \n183: **选择**：使用 Rich 美化输出，包括构建进度和结果\n184: \n185: **理由**：\n186: - 提供良好的用户体验\n187: - 清晰展示构建状态\n188: - 支持颜色和图标\n189: \n190: **实现**：\n191: ```python\n192: from rich.console import Console\n193: from rich.progress import Progress\n194: \n195: console = Console()\n196: with Progress() as progress:\n197:     task = progress.add_task(\"Building image...\", total=100)\n198:     # 构建进度更新\n199:     progress.update(task, advance=50)\n200: ```\n201: \n202: ## Alternatives Considered\n203: \n204: ### Alternative 1: 手动指定版本号\n205: \n206: **描述**：每次构建时手动指定版本号，不自动递增\n207: \n208: **优点**：\n209: - 用户完全控制版本号\n210: - 灵活性高\n211: \n212: **缺点**：\n213: - 增加用户负担\n214: - 容易出错\n215: - 版本号冲突\n216: \n217: **选择**：不采纳 - 自动递增更方便\n218: \n219: ### Alternative 2: 不支持云端构建\n220: \n221: **描述**：仅支持本地 Docker 构建\n222: \n223: **优点**：\n224: - 实现简单\n225: - 依赖少\n226: \n227: **缺点**：\n228: - 无法满足大规模部署需求\n229: - 无法利用云服务商优势\n230: \n231: **选择**：不采纳 - 云端构建是生产环境必需\n232: \n233: ### Alternative 3: 构建失败时不回滚版本\n234: \n235: **描述**：即使构建失败，也保留递增后的版本号\n236: \n237: **优点**：\n238: - 实现简单\n239: - 避免版本号重复\n240: \n241: **缺点**：\n242: - 版本号不一致\n243: - 用户困惑\n244: \n245: **选择**：不采纳 - 回滚机制保证一致性\n246: \n247: ## Implementation Plan\n248: \n249: ### Phase 1: BuildRuntime 基础框架 (Day 1)\n250: \n251: 1. 创建 `agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py` 文件\n252: 2. 实现 `BuildRuntime` 类基础结构\n253: 3. 实现 `__init__` 方法\n254: 4. 实现 `build()` 方法框架\n255: \n256: **代码框架**：\n257: ```python\n258: from pathlib import Path\n259: from typing import Any, Dict\n260: import logging\n261: \n262: from agentcube.services.docker_service import DockerService\n263: from agentcube.services.metadata_service import MetadataService\n264: \n265: logger = logging.getLogger(__name__)\n266: \n267: class BuildRuntime:\n268:     def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False) -> None:\n269:         self.verbose = verbose\n270:         self.docker_service = DockerService(verbose=verbose)\n271:         self.metadata_service = MetadataService(verbose=verbose)\n272: \n273:     def build(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n274:         \"\"\"Build container image from workspace.\"\"\"\n275:         # 实现构建逻辑\n276:         pass\n277: ```\n278: \n279: ### Phase 2: 版本管理实现 (Day 1)\n280: \n281: 1. 实现 `_increment_version()` 方法\n282: 2. 实现版本号解析和递增\n283: 3. 实现版本回滚机制\n284: \n285: **实现**：\n286: ```python\n287: import semver\n288: \n289: def _increment_version(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata) -> Any:\n290:     \"\"\"Increment version number and return original version.\"\"\"\n291:     original_version = metadata.version or \"0.0.0\"\n292:     if self.verbose:\n293:         logger.info(f\"Original version: {original_version}\")\n294: \n295:     # 解析版本号\n296:     try:\n297:         version_info = semver.VersionInfo.parse(original_version)\n298:     except ValueError:\n299:         # 如果版本号不符合语义化版本，添加 `.1` 后缀\n300:         new_version = f\"{original_version}.1\"\n301:     else:\n302:         # 递增 patch 版本\n303:         new_version = str(version_info.bump_patch())\n304: \n305:     if self.verbose:\n306:         logger.info(f\"New version: {new_version}\")\n307: \n308:     # 更新元数据\n309:     metadata.version = new_version\n310:     self.metadata_service.save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)\n311: \n312:     return original_version\n313: ```\n314: \n315: ### Phase 3: 前置条件验证 (Day 2)\n316: \n317: 1. 实现 `_validate_build_prerequisites()` 方法\n318: 2. 验证 Docker 守护进程可用性\n319: 3. 验证 Dockerfile 存在\n320: 4. 验证元数据完整性\n321: \n322: **实现**：\n323: ```python\n324: def _validate_build_prerequisites(self, workspace_path: Path) -> None:\n325:     \"\"\"Validate build prerequisites.\"\"\"\n326:     # 验证 Docker 可用性\n327:     if not self.docker_service.check_docker_available():\n328:         raise RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available or not running\")\n329: \n330:     # 验证 Dockerfile 存在\n331:     dockerfile_path = workspace_path / \"Dockerfile\"\n332:     if not dockerfile_path.exists():\n333:         raise FileNotFoundError(f\"Dockerfile not found: {dockerfile_path}\")\n334: \n335:     if self.verbose:\n336:         logger.info(f\"Dockerfile found: {dockerfile_path}\")\n337: ```\n338: \n339: ### Phase 4: 本地构建实现 (Day 2-3)\n340: \n341: 1. 实现 `_build_local()` 方法\n342: 2. 集成 Docker 服务\n343: 3. 支持代理配置\n344: 4. 返回构建结果\n345: \n346: **实现**：\n347: ```python\n348: def _build_local(\n349:     self,\n350:     workspace_path: Path,\n351:     metadata,\n352:     options: Dict[str, Any]\n353: ) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n354:     \"\"\"Build image using local Docker.\"\"\"\n355:     if self.verbose:\n356:         logger.info(\"Starting local build...\")\n357: \n358:     # 准备构建参数\n359:     build_args = {}\n360:     proxy = options.get(\"proxy\")\n361:     if proxy:\n362:         build_args[\"HTTP_PROXY\"] = proxy\n363:         build_args[\"HTTPS_PROXY\"] = proxy\n364:         if self.verbose:\n365:             logger.info(f\"Using proxy: {proxy}\")\n366: \n367:     # 准备镜像名称和标签\n368:     image_name = metadata.agent_name\n369:     tag = metadata.version or \"latest\"\n370:     dockerfile_path = workspace_path / \"Dockerfile\"\n371: \n372:     # 构建镜像\n373:     build_result = self.docker_service.build_image(\n374:         dockerfile_path=dockerfile_path,\n375:         context_path=workspace_path,\n376:         image_name=image_name,\n377:         tag=tag,\n378:         build_args=build_args if build_args else None\n379:     )\n380: \n381:     if self.verbose:\n382:         logger.info(f\"Build completed: {build_result}\")\n383: \n384:     # 更新元数据\n385:     self._update_build_metadata(\n386:         workspace_path,\n387:         metadata,\n388:         build_result,\n389:         tag\n390:     )\n391: \n392:     return build_result\n393: ```\n394: \n395: ### Phase 5: 云端构建实现 (Day 3-4)\n396: \n397: 1. 实现 `_build_cloud()` 方法\n398: 2. 集成云服务商 SDK\n399: 3. 支持华为云等云服务\n400: 4. 返回构建结果\n401: \n402: **实现**（框架）：\n403: ```python\n404: def _build_cloud(\n405:     self,\n406:     workspace_path: Path,\n407:     metadata,\n408:     options: Dict[str, Any]\n409: ) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n410:     \"\"\"Build image using cloud provider.\"\"\"\n411:     cloud_provider = options.get(\"cloud_provider\", \"huawei\")\n412: \n413:     if self.verbose:\n414:         logger.info(f\"Starting cloud build with provider: {cloud_provider}\")\n415: \n416:     if cloud_provider == \"huawei\":\n417:         return self._build_huawei_cloud(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n418:     else:\n419:         raise ValueError(f\"Unsupported cloud provider: {cloud_provider}\")\n420: \n421: def _build_huawei_cloud(\n422:     self,\n423:     workspace_path: Path,\n424:     metadata,\n425:     options: Dict[str, Any]\n426: ) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n427:     \"\"\"Build image using Huawei Cloud.\"\"\"\n428:     # 实现华为云构建逻辑\n429:     # TODO: 集成华为云 SDK\n430:     pass\n431: ```\n432: \n433: ### Phase 6: 元数据更新实现 (Day 4)\n434: \n435: 1. 实现 `_update_build_metadata()` 方法\n436: 2. 更新镜像信息\n437: 3. 更新构建时间\n438: 4. 持久化元数据\n439: \n440: **实现**：\n441: ```python\n442: from datetime import datetime\n443: \n444: def _update_build_metadata(\n445:     self,\n446:     workspace_path: Path,\n447:     metadata,\n448:     build_result: Dict[str, str],\n449:     tag: str = \"latest\"\n450: ) -> None:\n451:     \"\"\"Update metadata with build information.\"\"\"\n452:     # 更新镜像信息\n453:     metadata.image = {\n454:         \"name\": build_result.get(\"image_name\"),\n455:         \"id\": build_result.get(\"image_id\"),\n456:         \"size\": build_result.get(\"image_size\"),\n457:         \"tag\": tag,\n458:         \"build_time\": build_result.get(\"build_time\") or datetime.utcnow().isoformat()\n459:     }\n460: \n461:     # 保存元数据\n462:     self.metadata_service.save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)\n463: \n464:     if self.verbose:\n465:         logger.info(f\"Metadata updated: {metadata.image}\")\n466: ```\n467: \n468: ### Phase 7: CLI 命令集成 (Day 4)\n469: \n470: 1. 在 `agentcube/cli/main.py` 中添加 `build` 命令\n471: 2. 添加命令行参数\n472: 3. 集成 BuildRuntime\n473: 4. 实现错误处理\n474: \n475: **实现**：\n476: ```python\n477: import typer\n478: from pathlib import Path\n479: from agentcube.runtime.build_runtime import BuildRuntime\n480: \n481: def build(\n482:     workspace: str = typer.Option(\n483:         \".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\",\n484:         help=\"Path to the agent workspace directory\",\n485:         show_default=True\n486:     ),\n487:     proxy: Optional[str] = typer.Option(\n488:         None, \"-p\", \"--proxy\",\n489:         help=\"Custom proxy URL for dependency resolution\"\n490:     ),\n491:     cloud_provider: Optional[str] = typer.Option(\n492:         None, \"--cloud-provider\",\n493:         help=\"Cloud provider name (e.g., huawei)\"\n494:     ),\n495:     output: Optional[str] = typer.Option(\n496:         None, \"--output\",\n497:         help=\"Output path for build artifacts\"\n498:     ),\n499:     verbose: bool = typer.Option(\n500:         False, \"--verbose\",\n501:         help=\"Enable detailed logging\"\n502:     )\n503: ) -> None:\n504:     \"\"\"Build container image from packaged workspace.\"\"\"\n505:     workspace_path = Path(workspace)\n506: \n507:     try:\n508:         runtime = BuildRuntime(verbose=verbose)\n509:         result = runtime.build(\n510:             workspace_path=workspace_path,\n511:             proxy=proxy,\n512:             cloud_provider=cloud_provider,\n513:             output=output\n514:         )\n515: \n516:         # 输出构建结果\n517:         console = Console()\n518:         console.print(\"[green]✓[/green] Build completed successfully!\")\n519:         console.print(f\"  Image: {result.get('image_name')}:{result.get('tag')}\")\n520:         console.print(f\"  ID: {result.get('image_id')}\")\n521:         console.print(f\"  Size: {result.get('image_size')}\")\n522:         console.print(f\"  Time: {result.get('build_time')}\")\n523: \n524:     except Exception as e:\n525:         _handle_error(e, \"build\", verbose)\n526: ```\n527: \n528: ### Phase 8: 错误处理和回滚 (Day 4-5)\n529: \n530: 1. 实现构建失败时的版本回滚\n531: 2. 实现详细的错误信息输出\n532: 3. 实现日志记录\n533: \n534: **实现**：\n535: ```python\n536: def build(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n537:     \"\"\"Build container image from workspace.\"\"\"\n538:     # 加载元数据\n539:     metadata = self.metadata_service.load_metadata(workspace_path)\n540: \n541:     # 递增版本号\n542:     original_version = self._increment_version(workspace_path, metadata)\n543: \n544:     try:\n545:         # 验证前置条件\n546:         self._validate_build_prerequisites(workspace_path)\n547: \n548:         # 执行构建\n549:         build_mode = metadata.build_mode or \"local\"\n550:         if build_mode == \"local\":\n551:             result = self._build_local(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n552:         elif build_mode == \"cloud\":\n553:             result = self._build_cloud(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n554:         else:\n555:             raise ValueError(f\"Unsupported build mode: {build_mode}\")\n556: \n557:         return result\n558: \n559:     except Exception as e:\n560:         # 回滚版本号\n561:         if self.verbose:\n562:             logger.warning(f\"Build failed, rolling back version to {original_version}\")\n563: \n564:         metadata.version = original_version\n565:         self.metadata_service.save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)\n566: \n567:         raise\n568: ```\n569: \n570: ### Phase 9: 测试 (Day 5-6)\n571: \n572: 1. 单元测试\n573:    - 测试版本递增逻辑\n574:    - 测试前置条件验证\n575:    - 测试本地构建\n576:    - 测试错误处理\n577: \n578: 2. 集成测试\n579:    - 测试完整的构建流程\n580:    - 测试与 Docker 集成\n581:    - 测试元数据更新\n582: \n583: 3. 端到端测试\n584:    - 测试 `pack` → `build` → `publish` 链路\n585:    - 测试构建失败回滚\n586: \n587: ### Phase 10: 文档 (Day 6)\n588: \n589: 1. 更新 CLI 文档\n590: 2. 添加使用示例\n591: 3. 添加故障排查指南\n592: 4. 更新 README\n593: \n594: ## Testing Strategy\n595: \n596: ### Unit Tests\n597: \n598: 1. **版本管理测试**\n599:    - 测试正常版本号递增\n600:    - 测试无效版本号处理\n601:    - 测试版本回滚\n602: \n603: 2. **前置条件验证测试**\n604:    - 测试 Docker 可用性检查\n605:    - 测试 Dockerfile 存在检查\n606:    - 测试元数据完整性检查\n607: \n608: 3. **本地构建测试**\n609:    - 测试成功构建\n610:    - 测试代理配置\n611:    - 测试构建失败\n612: \n613: 4. **错误处理测试**\n614:    - 测试版本回滚\n615:    - 测试错误信息输出\n616:    - 测试日志记录\n617: \n618: ### Integration Tests\n619: \n620: 1. **Docker 集成测试**\n621:    - 测试真实 Docker 构建\n622:    - 测试构建参数传递\n623:    - 测试构建结果解析\n624: \n625: 2. **元数据集成测试**\n626:    - 测试元数据加载\n627:    - 测试元数据更新\n628:    - 测试元数据持久化\n629: \n630: 3. **完整流程测试**\n631:    - 测试 `pack` → `build` 链路\n632:    - 测试 `build` → `publish` 链路\n633:    - 测试完整生命周期\n634: \n635: ### Test Coverage\n636: \n637: 目标：> 80% 代码覆盖率\n638: \n639: ## Configuration\n640: \n641: ### 命令行参数\n642: \n643: | 参数 | 类型 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n644: |------|------|--------|------|\n645: | `--workspace` / `-f` | str | `\".\"` | 工作空间路径 |\n646: | `--proxy` / `-p` | str | `None` | 代理 URL |\n647: | `--cloud-provider` | str | `None` | 云服务提供商 |\n648: | `--output` | str | `None` | 输出路径 |\n649: | `--verbose` | bool | `False` | 详细日志 |\n650: \n651: ### 元数据配置\n652: \n653: 在 `agent_metadata.yaml` 中：\n654: \n655: ```yaml\n656: agent_name: \"my-agent\"\n657: version: \"0.1.0\"\n658: build_mode: \"local\"  # 或 \"cloud\"\n659: ```\n660: \n661: ### 环境变量\n662: \n663: | 变量 | 说明 |\n664: |------|------|\n665: | `DOCKER_HOST` | Docker 守护进程地址 |\n666: | `HTTP_PROXY` | HTTP 代理 |\n667: | `HTTPS_PROXY` | HTTPS 代理 |\n668: | `NO_PROXY` | 不使用代理的主机 |\n669: \n670: ## API Specification\n671: \n672: ### build() 方法签名\n673: \n674: ```python\n675: def build(\n676:     workspace_path: Path,\n677:     proxy: Optional[str] = None,\n678:     cloud_provider: Optional[str] = None,\n679:     output: Optional[str] = None,\n680:     verbose: bool = False\n681: ) -> Dict[str, Any]\n682: ```\n683: \n684: ### 返回值\n685: \n686: ```python\n687: {\n688:     \"image_name\": \"my-agent\",\n689:     \"image_id\": \"sha256:abc123...\",\n690:     \"image_size\": \"150MB\",\n691:     \"tag\": \"0.1.1\",\n692:     \"build_time\": \"2024-01-15T10:30:00Z\"\n693: }\n694: ```\n695: \n696: ### 异常\n697: \n698: - `RuntimeError` - Docker 不可用\n699: - `FileNotFoundError` - Dockerfile 不存在\n700: - `ValueError` - 无效的构建模式或云服务提供商\n701: - `Exception` - 其他构建错误\n702: \n703: ## Security Considerations\n704: \n705: 1. **Docker 守护进程安全**\n706:    - 验证 Docker 守护进程连接\n707:    - 避免构建特权容器\n708:    - 限制 Docker 访问权限\n709: \n710: 2. **代理安全**\n711:    - 支持安全代理（HTTPS）\n712:    - 避免在日志中输出代理凭证\n713:    - 支持环境变量配置\n714: \n715: 3. **元数据安全**\n716:    - 避免在元数据中存储敏感信息\n717:    - 确保文件权限正确\n718:    - 支持元数据加密（可选）\n719: \n720: 4. **云构建安全**\n721:    - 支持云服务认证\n722:    - 避免硬编码凭证\n723:    - 支持凭证轮换\n724: \n725: ## Performance Considerations\n726: \n727: 1. **构建性能**\n728:    - 利用 Docker 缓存层\n729:    - 支持并行构建（可选）\n730:    - 优化 Dockerfile 指令顺序\n731: \n732: 2. **资源使用**\n733:    - 控制构建内存使用\n734:    - 限制构建并发数\n735:    - 支持构建超时\n736: \n737: 3. **网络性能**\n738:    - 支持代理加速\n739:    - 支持镜像缓存\n740:    - 优化依赖下载\n741: \n742: ## Monitoring and Metrics\n743: \n744: ### 日志记录\n745: \n746: 使用 Python 标准库 `logging`：\n747: \n748: - 构建开始/结束\n749: - 版本变更\n750: - 错误信息\n751: - 调试信息（verbose 模式）\n752: \n753: ### 构建指标\n754: \n755: - 构建时间\n756: - 镜像大小\n757: - 构建成功率\n758: - 构建失败原因\n759: \n760: ## Open Questions\n761: \n762: 1. **Q1**: 是否需要支持多架构构建？\n763:    - **当前**: 不支持\n764:    - **讨论**: 支持 AMD64、ARM64 等多架构\n765:    - **决策**: 初始不支持，后续根据需求添加\n766: \n767: 2. **Q2**: 云端构建是否需要支持多个云服务商？\n768:    - **当前**: 仅支持华为云\n769:    - **讨论**: 支持阿里云、AWS 等\n770:    - **决策**: 初始仅支持华为云，后续扩展\n771: \n772: 3. **Q3**: 是否需要支持构建缓存？\n773:    - **当前**: 使用 Docker 默认缓存\n774:    - **讨论**: 自定义缓存策略\n775:    - **决策**: 初始使用 Docker 缓存，后续优化\n776: \n777: 4. **Q4**: 是否需要支持构建进度通知？\n778:    - **当前**: 仅日志输出\n779:    - **讨论**: Webhook、邮件通知等\n780:    - **决策**: 初始不支持，后续根据需求添加\n781: \n782: ## Next Steps\n783: \n784: 1. 创建 BuildRuntime 类\n785: 2. 实现版本管理功能\n786: 3. 实现本地 Docker 构建\n787: 4. 实现 CLI 命令集成\n788: 5. 编写单元测试和集成测试\n789: 6. 更新文档\n790: 7. 集成到 CI/CD 流程\n791: \n792: ## References\n793: \n794: - [AgentCube CLI Design](../cli-toolkit/design.md)\n795: - [AgentCube CLI Spec](../cli-toolkit/spec.md)\n796: - [Docker SDK for Python](https://docker-py.readthedocs.io/)\n797: - [SemVer](https://semver.org/)\n798: - [Typer Documentation](https://typer.tiangolo.com/)\n\n(End of file - total 798 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-021: CLI build 命令\n\n## Overview\n\n实现 AgentCube CLI 的 `build` 命令，用于从打包好的工作空间构建容器镜像。该命令支持本地 Docker 构建和云端构建两种模式，能够自动管理版本号、验证构建前置条件，并集成 Docker 服务进行镜像构建。\n\n## Purpose\n\n提供 `kubectl-agentcube build` 命令，实现：\n\n1. **本地 Docker 构建**：使用本地 Docker 守护进程构建容器镜像\n2. **云端构建**：集成云服务商（如华为云）的构建服务\n3. **版本管理**：自动递增版本号（patch 级别），构建失败时回滚版本\n4. **代理支持**：支持自定义代理 URL 进行依赖解析\n5. **构建结果输出**：输出镜像名称、ID、大小等构建信息\n6. **元数据更新**：更新 `agent_metadata.yaml` 中的构建信息\n\n## Module\n\n`cmd/cli` - AgentCube CLI 工具包","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775867342659,"end":1775867342668}}}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775867342697,"sessionID":"ses_2860fd53cffeIZwy9rcWI6qt9T","part":{"id":"prt_d79f12f4e001Cixi7ECcaTsUWC","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d79f1277f001ZQrRJSi0TRE57G","sessionID":"ses_2860fd53cffeIZwy9rcWI6qt9T","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":35334,"input":199,"output":64,"reasoning":0,"cache":{"write":0,"read":35071}},"cost":0}}
{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775867345625,"sessionID":"ses_2860fd53cffeIZwy9rcWI6qt9T","part":{"id":"prt_d79f13ad6001me9XSV0vYdhhxV","messageID":"msg_d79f12f81001rCedTpkDq5vQ02","sessionID":"ses_2860fd53cffeIZwy9rcWI6qt9T","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775867462263,"sessionID":"ses_2860fd53cffeIZwy9rcWI6qt9T","part":{"id":"prt_d79f301050019OGP47GiJVR9Fu","messageID":"msg_d79f12f81001rCedTpkDq5vQ02","sessionID":"ses_2860fd53cffeIZwy9rcWI6qt9T","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-1aa2f94e3797426c943c1924a988f147","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-022: CLI publish 命令\n\n## Overview\n\n实现 AgentCube CLI 的 `publish` 命令，用于将构建好的容器镜像发布到 Kubernetes 集群。该命令支持两种发布方式：AgentCube 自定义资源（AgentRuntime CR）和标准 Kubernetes 资源（Deployment + Service），能够处理镜像推送、资源部署和元数据更新。\n\n## Purpose\n\n提供 `kubectl-agentcube publish` 命令，实现：\n\n1. **镜像准备**：支持本地镜像推送到容器注册表，或使用云端构建的镜像 URL\n2. **AgentCube 提供商**：部署到 AgentRuntime 自定义资源，集成工作负载管理器和路由器\n3. **标准 K8s 提供商**：部署到标准的 Deployment 和 NodePort Service\n4. **版本管理**：支持语义化版本号，更新元数据中的部署信息\n5. **部署配置**：支持命名空间、副本数、节点端口等配置\n6. **状态验证**：等待部署就绪，提供详细的部署状态反馈\n\n## Module\n\n`cmd/cli` - AgentCube CLI 工具包\n\n## Language\n\nPython 3.10+\n\n## Size\n\nL\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n1. **PublishRuntime 类实现** (`agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py`)\n   - `publish()` 主方法，支持两种提供商\n   - `_publish_cr_to_k8s()` - AgentRuntime CR 部署\n   - `_publish_k8s()` - 标准 K8s 资源部署\n   - `_prepare_image_for_publishing()` - 镜像准备\n   - `_prepare_local_image()` - 本地镜像推送\n   - `_prepare_cloud_image()` - 云端镜像验证\n   - `_update_publish_metadata()` - 更新发布元数据\n\n2. **CLI 命令集成** (`agentcube/cli/main.py`)\n   - `publish()` Typer 命令函数\n   - 命令行参数：`--workspace`, `--version`, `--image-url`, `--provider`, `--namespace`, `--replicas`, `--node-port`, `--region`, `--cloud-provider`, `--description`, `--verbose`\n   - 错误处理和用户反馈\n\n3. **AgentCube 提供商** (`agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py`)\n   - `deploy_agent_runtime()` - 部署 AgentRuntime CR\n   - 设置默认会话超时\n   - 配置工作负载管理器和路由器 URL\n\n4. **Kubernetes 提供商** (`agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py`)\n   - `deploy_agent()` - 部署 Deployment 和 Service\n   - `wait_for_deployment_ready()` - 等待部署就绪\n   - 支持节点端口配置\n\n5. **Docker 服务集成** (`agentcube/services/docker_service.py`)\n   - `push_image()` - 推送镜像到注册表\n   - 镜像标记和凭证管理\n\n6. **元数据服务集成** (`agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`)\n   - 加载和保存 `agent_metadata.yaml`\n   - 部署信息持久化\n\n### Out of Scope\n\n- 容器注册表管理（使用已有服务）\n- Kubernetes 集群安装和配置\n- 镜像构建功能（由 `build` 命令完成）\n- 工作空间打包功能（由 `pack` 命令完成）\n\n## Impact Analysis\n\n### Components Impacted\n\n1. **CLI 工具包** (`cmd/cli`)\n   - 添加 `publish` 命令到 Typer 应用\n   - 新增 `PublishRuntime` 类\n   - 更新导入和依赖\n\n2. **Kubernetes 客户端**\n   - 集成 `kubernetes` Python 客户端库\n   - 支持 AgentRuntime CRD 操作\n   - 支持标准 K8s 资源操作\n\n3. **Docker 服务**\n   - 确保已实现 `push_image()` 方法\n   - 支持镜像标记和推送\n\n4. **提供商服务**\n   - `AgentCubeProvider` 用于 AgentRuntime CR 部署\n   - `KubernetesProvider` 用于标准 K8s 部署\n\n5. **用户工作流**\n   - `pack` → `build` → `publish` → `invoke` 的完整链路\n   - 元数据文件在命令间传递状态\n\n### Dependencies\n\n**核心依赖**（已在 `pyproject.toml` 中定义）：\n- `typer[all]>=0.9.0` - CLI 框架\n- `pydantic>=2.0.0` - 数据验证\n- `pyyaml>=6.0` - YAML 解析\n- `docker>=6.0.0` - Docker SDK\n- `rich>=13.0.0` - 美化输出\n- `kubernetes>=28.0.0` - Kubernetes 客户端\n\n**可选依赖**：\n- `httpx>=0.24.0` - HTTP 客户端\n\n### Security Considerations\n\n1. **镜像凭证安全**\n   - 支持安全的镜像注册表认证（HTTPS）\n   - 避免在日志中输出凭证\n   - 支持凭证轮换\n\n2. **Kubernetes 访问安全**\n   - 验证 kubeconfig 配置\n   - 支持命名空间隔离\n   - 避免权限提升\n\n3. **元数据安全**\n   - 避免在元数据中存储敏感信息\n   - 确保文件权限正确\n   - 支持元数据加密（可选）\n\n4. **部署安全**\n   - 验证镜像来源\n   - 支持镜像签名验证（可选）\n   - 限制资源使用\n\n## Design Decisions\n\n### 提供商选择策略\n\n**选择**：支持 AgentCube（AgentRuntime CR）和标准 K8s（Deployment + Service）两种提供商\n\n**理由**：\n- AgentCube 提供商：利用 AgentCube 特性（会话管理、工作负载管理器、路由器）\n- 标准 K8s 提供商：兼容标准 Kubernetes 集群\n- 满足不同部署场景需求\n\n**实现**：\n```python\nif provider == \"agentcube\":\n    result = self._publish_cr_to_k8s(workspace_path, metadata, **options)\nelif provider == \"k8s\":\n    result = self._publish_k8s(workspace_path, metadata, **options)\nelse:\n    raise ValueError(f\"Unsupported provider: {provider}\")\n```\n\n### 镜像准备策略\n\n**选择**：根据构建模式选择镜像准备方式\n\n**理由**：\n- 本地构建模式：需要推送镜像到注册表\n- 云端构建模式：直接使用云端镜像 URL\n- 灵活支持不同构建场景\n\n**实现**：\n```python\ndef _prepare_image_for_publishing(\n    self,\n    workspace_path: Path,\n    metadata,\n    options: Dict[str, Any]\n) -> str:\n    \"\"\"Prepare image for publishing.\"\"\"\n    build_mode = metadata.build_mode or \"local\"\n\n    if build_mode == \"local\":\n        return self._prepare_local_image(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n    elif build_mode == \"cloud\":\n        return self._prepare_cloud_image(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n    else:\n        raise ValueError(f\"Unsupported build mode: {build_mode}\")\n```\n\n### 版本管理策略\n\n**选择**：使用语义化版本号，支持版本覆盖\n\n**理由**：\n- 符合软件版本管理最佳实践\n- 便于版本追踪和回滚\n- 支持多版本并存\n\n**实现**：\n```python\nversion = options.get(\"version\") or metadata.version\nif not version:\n    raise ValueError(\"Version must be specified either via --version or in metadata\")\n\n# 更新元数据中的版本\nmetadata.version = version\nself.metadata_service.save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)\n```\n\n### 部署验证策略\n\n**选择**：等待部署就绪，提供实时状态反馈\n\n**理由**：\n- 确保部署成功后才返回\n- 提供用户友好的进度反馈\n- 便于问题诊断\n\n**实现**：\n```python\n# 等待部署就绪\nif provider == \"k8s\":\n    k8s_provider = KubernetesProvider(\n        namespace=namespace,\n        verbose=self.verbose\n    )\n    k8s_provider.wait_for_deployment_ready(\n        deployment_name,\n        timeout=120\n    )\n```\n\n## Alternatives Considered\n\n### Alternative 1: 仅支持 AgentCube 提供商\n\n**描述**：仅支持 AgentRuntime CR 部署，不支持标准 K8s 资源\n\n**优点**：\n- 实现简单\n- 充分利用 AgentCube 特性\n- 统一的部署体验\n\n**缺点**：\n- 不兼容标准 Kubernetes 集群\n- 限制部署场景\n- 增加用户迁移成本\n\n**选择**：不采纳 - 需要支持标准 K8s 以提高兼容性\n\n### Alternative 2: 不支持镜像推送\n\n**描述**：仅支持使用云端镜像 URL，不支持本地镜像推送\n\n**优点**：\n- 实现简单\n- 避免镜像管理复杂性\n\n**缺点**：\n- 无法满足本地构建需求\n- 增加部署成本\n- 限制灵活性\n\n**选择**：不采纳 - 镜像推送是本地构建的必要功能\n\n### Alternative 3: 不等待部署就绪\n\n**描述**：提交部署请求后立即返回，不等待部署就绪\n\n**优点**：\n- 响应速度快\n- 实现简单\n\n**缺点**：\n- 无法确认部署成功\n- 错误诊断困难\n- 用户体验差\n\n**选择**：不采纳 - 等待部署就绪是必要的\n\n## Implementation Plan\n\n### Phase 1: PublishRuntime 基础框架 (Day 1-2)\n\n1. 创建 `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` 文件\n2. 实现 `PublishRuntime` 类基础结构\n3. 实现 `__init__` 方法\n4. 实现 `publish()` 方法框架\n\n**代码框架**：\n```python\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any, Dict, Optional\nimport logging\n\nfrom agentcube.services.docker_service import DockerService\nfrom agentcube.services.metadata_service import MetadataService\nfrom agentcube.services.agentcube_provider import AgentCubeProvider\nfrom agentcube.services.k8s_provider import KubernetesProvider\n\nlogger = logging.getLogger(__name__)\n\nclass PublishRuntime:\n    def __init__(self, verbose: bool = False, provider: str = \"agentcube\") -> None:\n        self.verbose = verbose\n        self.provider = provider\n        self.docker_service = DockerService(verbose=verbose)\n        self.metadata_service = MetadataService(verbose=verbose)\n\n    def publish(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n        \"\"\"Publish agent to Kubernetes.\"\"\"\n        # 实现发布逻辑\n        pass\n```\n\n### Phase 2: 镜像准备实现 (Day 2-3)\n\n1. 实现 `_prepare_image_for_publishing()` 方法\n2. 实现 `_prepare_local_image()` 方法\n3. 实现 `_prepare_cloud_image()` 方法\n\n**实现**：\n```python\ndef _prepare_image_for_publishing(\n    self,\n    workspace_path: Path,\n    metadata,\n    options: Dict[str, Any]\n) -> str:\n    \"\"\"Prepare image for publishing.\"\"\"\n    build_mode = metadata.build_mode or \"local\"\n\n    if self.verbose:\n        logger.info(f\"Preparing image for {build_mode} build mode\")\n\n    if build_mode == \"local\":\n        return self._prepare_local_image(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n    elif build_mode == \"cloud\":\n        return self._prepare_cloud_image(workspace_path, metadata, options)\n    else:\n        raise ValueError(f\"Unsupported build mode: {build_mode}\")\n\ndef _prepare_local_image(\n    self,\n    workspace_path: Path,\n    metadata,\n    options: Dict[str, Any]\n) -> str:\n    \"\"\"Prepare local image by pushing to registry.\"\"\"\n    # 获取镜像信息\n    image_info = metadata.image\n    if not image_info:\n        raise ValueError(\"No image information found in metadata\")\n\n    image_name = image_info.get(\"name\")\n    tag = metadata.version or image_info.get(\"tag\", \"latest\")\n\n    # 检查是否需要推送到注册表\n    image_url = options.get(\"image_url\")\n    registry_url = metadata.registry_url or \"\"\n\n    if not registry_url and not image_url:\n        raise ValueError(\n            \"Image URL must be specified via --image-url for local build mode, \"\n            \"or registry_url must be set in agent_metadata.yaml\"\n        )\n\n    # 构建完整的镜像 URL\n    full_image_url = image_url or f\"{registry_url}/{image_name}:{tag}\"\n\n    if self.verbose:\n        logger.info(f\"Pushing image to registry: {full_image_url}\")\n\n    # 推送镜像\n    push_result = self.docker_service.push_image(\n        image_name=image_name,\n        tag=tag,\n        registry_url=registry_url,\n        username=options.get(\"image_username\") or metadata.registry_username,\n        password=options.get(\"image_password\") or metadata.registry_password\n    )\n\n    if self.verbose:\n        logger.info(f\"Image pushed successfully: {push_result}\")\n\n    return full_image_url\n\ndef _prepare_cloud_image(\n    self,\n    workspace_path: Path,\n    metadata,\n    options: Dict[str, Any]\n) -> str:\n    \"\"\"Prepare cloud image URL.\"\"\"\n    image_url = options.get(\"image_url\")\n\n    if not image_url:\n        raise ValueError(\n            \"Image URL must be specified via --image-url for cloud build mode\"\n        )\n\n    if self.verbose:\n        logger.info(f\"Using cloud image URL: {image_url}\")\n\n    return image_url\n```\n\n### Phase 3: AgentCube 提供商实现 (Day 3-4)\n\n1. 实现 `_publish_cr_to_k8s()` 方法\n2. 验证前置条件\n3. 调用 AgentCubeProvider 部署\n4. 更新元数据\n\n**实现**：\n```python\ndef _publish_cr_to_k8s(\n    self,\n    workspace_path: Path,\n    metadata,\n    **options: Any\n) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n    \"\"\"Publish using AgentRuntime CR.\"\"\"\n    # 验证前置条件\n    if not metadata.router_url:\n        raise ValueError(\n            \"router_url is required in agent_metadata.yaml for agentcube provider\"\n        )\n    if not metadata.workload_manager_url:\n        raise ValueError(\n            \"workload_manager_url is required in agent_metadata.yaml for agentcube provider\"\n        )\n\n    # 准备镜像 URL\n    image_url = self._prepare_image_for_publishing(\n        workspace_path, metadata, options\n    )\n\n    if self.verbose:\n        logger.info(\"Deploying to AgentCube provider...\")\n\n    # 创建 AgentCubeProvider\n    namespace = options.get(\"namespace\") or \"default\"\n    agentcube_provider = AgentCubeProvider(\n        namespace=namespace,\n        verbose=self.verbose\n    )\n\n    # 部署 AgentRuntime CR\n    deploy_result = agentcube_provider.deploy_agent_runtime(\n        agent_name=metadata.agent_name,\n        image_url=image_url,\n        port=metadata.port,\n        entrypoint=metadata.entrypoint,\n        env_vars=None,\n        workload_manager_url=metadata.workload_manager_url,\n        router_url=metadata.router_url,\n        readiness_probe_path=metadata.readiness_probe_path,\n        readiness_probe_port=metadata.readiness_probe_port\n    )\n\n    if self.verbose:\n        logger.info(f\"AgentRuntime CR deployed: {deploy_result}\")\n\n    # 更新元数据\n    agent_info = {\n        \"agent_id\": deploy_result.get(\"agent_id\"),\n        \"agent_endpoint\": deploy_result.get(\"agent_endpoint\"),\n        \"deployment_type\": \"AgentRuntime\",\n        \"namespace\": namespace\n    }\n\n    self._update_publish_metadata(workspace_path, agent_info)\n\n    return deploy_result\n```\n\n### Phase 4: K8s 提供商实现 (Day 4-5)\n\n1. 实现 `_publish_k8s()` 方法\n2. 验证前置条件\n3. 调用 KubernetesProvider 部署\n4. 等待部署就绪\n5. 更新元数据\n\n**实现**：\n```python\ndef _publish_k8s(\n    self,\n    workspace_path: Path,\n    metadata,\n    **options: Any\n) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n    \"\"\"Publish using standard K8s resources.\"\"\"\n    # 准备镜像 URL\n    image_url = self._prepare_image_for_publishing(\n        workspace_path, metadata, options\n    )\n\n    if self.verbose:\n        logger.info(\"Deploying to Kubernetes provider...\")\n\n    # 创建 KubernetesProvider\n    namespace = options.get(\"namespace\") or \"default\"\n    k8s_provider = KubernetesProvider(\n        namespace=namespace,\n        verbose=self.verbose\n    )\n\n    # 部署 Deployment 和 Service\n    deploy_result = k8s_provider.deploy_agent(\n        agent_name=metadata.agent_name,\n        image_url=image_url,\n        port=metadata.port,\n        entrypoint=metadata.entrypoint,\n        replicas=options.get(\"replicas\", 1),\n        node_port=options.get(\"node_port\"),\n        env_vars=None\n    )\n\n    if self.verbose:\n        logger.info(f\"K8s resources created: {deploy_result}\")\n\n    # 等待部署就绪\n    deployment_name = deploy_result.get(\"deployment_name\")\n    try:\n        k8s_provider.wait_for_deployment_ready(\n            deployment_name,\n            timeout=120\n        )\n        if self.verbose:\n            logger.info(f\"Deployment {deployment_name} is ready\")\n    except TimeoutError as e:\n        error_msg = f\"Deployment {deployment_name} failed to become ready within timeout\"\n        logger.error(error_msg)\n        # 更新元数据记录错误\n        agent_info = {\n            \"deployment_type\": \"K8s\",\n            \"namespace\": namespace,\n            \"status\": \"error\",\n            \"error\": str(e)\n        }\n        self._update_publish_metadata(workspace_path, agent_info)\n        raise RuntimeError(error_msg) from e\n\n    # 更新元数据\n    agent_info = {\n        \"deployment_type\": \"K8s\",\n        \"namespace\": namespace,\n        \"deployment_name\": deploy_result.get(\"deployment_name\"),\n        \"service_name\": deploy_result.get(\"service_name\"),\n        \"service_url\": deploy_result.get(\"service_url\"),\n        \"node_port\": deploy_result.get(\"node_port\"),\n        \"replicas\": deploy_result.get(\"replicas\"),\n        \"status\": \"deployed\"\n    }\n\n    self._update_publish_metadata(workspace_path, agent_info)\n\n    return deploy_result\n```\n\n### Phase 5: 元数据更新实现 (Day 5)\n\n1. 实现 `_update_publish_metadata()` 方法\n2. 更新部署信息\n3. 持久化元数据\n\n**实现**：\n```python\ndef _update_publish_metadata(\n    self,\n    workspace_path: Path,\n    agent_info: Dict[str, Any]\n) -> None:\n    \"\"\"Update metadata with publish information.\"\"\"\n    # 加载元数据\n    metadata = self.metadata_service.load_metadata(workspace_path)\n\n    # 更新部署信息\n    metadata.k8s_deployment = agent_info\n    if \"agent_id\" in agent_info:\n        metadata.agent_id = agent_info[\"agent_id\"]\n    if \"agent_endpoint\" in agent_info:\n        metadata.agent_endpoint = agent_info[\"agent_endpoint\"]\n\n    # 保存元数据\n    self.metadata_service.save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)\n\n    if self.verbose:\n        logger.info(f\"Metadata updated with publish info: {agent_info}\")\n```\n\n### Phase 6: CLI 命令集成 (Day 5-6)\n\n1. 在 `agentcube/cli/main.py` 中添加 `publish` 命令\n2. 添加命令行参数\n3. 集成 PublishRuntime\n4. 实现错误处理和 Rich 输出\n\n**实现**：\n```python\nimport typer\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Optional, List\nfrom rich.console import Console\nfrom rich.table import Table\n\nfrom agentcube.runtime.publish_runtime import PublishRuntime\n\ndef publish(\n    workspace: str = typer.Option(\n        \".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\",\n        help=\"Path to the agent workspace directory\",\n        show_default=True\n    ),\n    version: Optional[str] = typer.Option(\n        None, \"--version\",\n        help=\"Semantic version string (e.g., v1.0.0)\"\n    ),\n    image_url: Optional[str] = typer.Option(\n        None, \"--image-url\",\n        help=\"Image repository URL (required in local build mode)\"\n    ),\n    image_username: Optional[str] = typer.Option(\n        None, \"--image-username\",\n        help=\"Username for image repository\"\n    ),\n    image_password: Optional[str] = typer.Option(\n        None, \"--image-password\",\n        help=\"Password for image repository\"\n    ),\n    description: Optional[str] = typer.Option(\n        None, \"--description\",\n        help=\"Agent description\"\n    ),\n    region: Optional[str] = typer.Option(\n        None, \"--region\",\n        help=\"Deployment region\"\n    ),\n    cloud_provider: Optional[str] = typer.Option(\n        None, \"--cloud-provider\",\n        help=\"Cloud provider name (e.g., huawei)\"\n    ),\n    provider: str = typer.Option(\n        \"agentcube\", \"--provider\",\n        help=\"Target provider: 'agentcube' (AgentRuntime CR) or 'k8s' (Deployment/Service)\"\n    ),\n    node_port: Optional[int] = typer.Option(\n        None, \"--node-port\",\n        help=\"Specific NodePort to use (30000-32767) for K8s deployment\"\n    ),\n    replicas: Optional[int] = typer.Option(\n        None, \"--replicas\",\n        help=\"Number of replicas for K8s deployment (default: 1)\"\n    ),\n    namespace: Optional[str] = typer.Option(\n        None, \"--namespace\",\n        help=\"The namespace for the deployment\"\n    ),\n    verbose: bool = typer.Option(\n        False, \"--verbose\",\n        help=\"Enable detailed logging\"\n    )\n) -> None:\n    \"\"\"Publish agent to Kubernetes.\"\"\"\n    workspace_path = Path(workspace)\n\n    try:\n        runtime = PublishRuntime(verbose=verbose, provider=provider)\n\n        # 准备选项\n        options = {\n            \"version\": version,\n            \"image_url\": image_url,\n            \"image_username\": image_username,\n            \"image_password\": image_password,\n            \"description\": description,\n            \"region\": region,\n            \"cloud_provider\": cloud_provider,\n            \"provider\": provider,\n            \"node_port\": node_port,\n            \"replicas\": replicas,\n            \"namespace\": namespace\n        }\n\n        # 执行发布\n        result = runtime.publish(workspace_path=workspace_path, **options)\n\n        # 输出成功信息\n        console = Console()\n        console.print(\"[green]✓[/green] Agent published successfully!\")\n\n        # 创建结果表格\n        table = Table(title=\"Deployment Information\")\n        table.add_column(\"Field\", style=\"cyan\")\n        table.add_column(\"Value\", style=\"green\")\n\n        table.add_row(\"Provider\", provider)\n        table.add_row(\"Agent Name\", result.get(\"agent_name\", \"\"))\n        table.add_row(\"Namespace\", result.get(\"namespace\", \"\"))\n\n        if provider == \"agentcube\":\n            table.add_row(\"Agent ID\", result.get(\"agent_id\", \"\"))\n            table.add_row(\"Endpoint\", result.get(\"agent_endpoint\", \"\"))\n        else:\n            table.add_row(\"Deployment\", result.get(\"deployment_name\", \"\"))\n            table.add_row(\"Service\", result.get(\"service_name\", \"\"))\n            table.add_row(\"Service URL\", result.get(\"service_url\", \"\"))\n            if result.get(\"node_port\"):\n                table.add_row(\"Node Port\", str(result.get(\"node_port\")))\n\n        console.print(table)\n\n    except Exception as e:\n        _handle_error(e, \"publish\", verbose)\n```\n\n### Phase 7: 提供商服务完善 (Day 6-7)\n\n1. 完善 `AgentCubeProvider.deploy_agent_runtime()` 方法\n2. 完善 `KubernetesProvider.deploy_agent()` 方法\n3. 添加必要的错误处理\n\n**AgentCubeProvider 实现**：\n```python\ndef deploy_agent_runtime(\n    self,\n    agent_name: str,\n    image_url: str,\n    port: int,\n    entrypoint: Optional[str] = None,\n    env_vars: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None,\n    workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = None,\n    router_url: Optional[str] = None,\n    readiness_probe_path: Optional[str] = None,\n    readiness_probe_port: Optional[int] = None\n) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n    \"\"\"Deploy agent using AgentRuntime CR.\"\"\"\n    # 创建 CR 规范\n    cr_spec = {\n        \"apiVersion\": \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\",\n        \"kind\": \"AgentRuntime\",\n        \"metadata\": {\n            \"name\": self._sanitize_name(agent_name),\n            \"namespace\": self.namespace\n        },\n        \"spec\": {\n            \"image\": image_url,\n            \"port\": port,\n            \"entrypoint\": entrypoint,\n            \"env\": env_vars or {},\n            \"sessionTimeout\": \"15m\",\n            \"maxSessionDuration\": \"8h\",\n            \"readinessProbe\": {\n                \"path\": readiness_probe_path or \"/health\",\n                \"port\": readiness_probe_port or port\n            }\n        }\n    }\n\n    # 嵌入工作负载管理器和路由器 URL\n    if workload_manager_url:\n        cr_spec[\"spec\"][\"env\"][\"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\"] = workload_manager_url\n    if router_url:\n        cr_spec[\"spec\"][\"env\"][\"ROUTER_URL\"] = router_url\n\n    # 添加 imagePullSecrets\n    cr_spec[\"spec\"][\"imagePullSecrets\"] = [{\"name\": \"default-secret\"}]\n\n    if self.verbose:\n        logger.info(f\"Creating AgentRuntime CR: {cr_spec}\")\n\n    # 使用 Kubernetes 客户端创建 CR\n    # TODO: 实现 CR 创建逻辑\n    pass\n\n    return {\n        \"agent_id\": cr_spec[\"metadata\"][\"name\"],\n        \"agent_endpoint\": f\"http://{cr_spec['metadata']['name']}.{self.namespace}.svc.cluster.local:{port}\",\n        \"namespace\": self.namespace\n    }\n```\n\n### Phase 8: 错误处理和验证 (Day 7-8)\n\n1. 实现详细的错误信息\n2. 添加输入验证\n3. 实现日志记录\n\n**验证逻辑**：\n```python\ndef publish(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n    \"\"\"Publish agent to Kubernetes.\"\"\"\n    # 加载元数据\n    metadata = self.metadata_service.load_metadata(workspace_path)\n\n    # 验证版本\n    version = options.get(\"version\") or metadata.version\n    if not version:\n        raise ValueError(\n            \"Version must be specified either via --version or in metadata\"\n        )\n\n    # 更新元数据版本\n    metadata.version = version\n    self.metadata_service.save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)\n\n    # 根据提供商选择部署方式\n    provider = options.get(\"provider\", self.provider)\n\n    if provider == \"agentcube\":\n        return self._publish_cr_to_k8s(workspace_path, metadata, **options)\n    elif provider == \"k8s\":\n        return self._publish_k8s(workspace_path, metadata, **options)\n    else:\n        raise ValueError(f\"Unsupported provider: {provider}\")\n```\n\n### Phase 9: 测试 (Day 8-10)\n\n1. 单元测试\n   - 测试镜像准备逻辑\n   - 测试 AgentCube 提供商\n   - 测试 K8s 提供商\n   - 测试错误处理\n\n2. 集成测试\n   - 测试完整的发布流程\n   - 测试与 Docker 集成\n   - 测试与 Kubernetes 集成\n   - 测试元数据更新\n\n3. 端到端测试\n   - 测试 `pack` → `build` → `publish` 链路\n   - 测试 `publish` → `invoke` 链路\n   - 测试完整生命周期\n\n### Phase 10: 文档 (Day 10)\n\n1. 更新 CLI 文档\n2. 添加使用示例\n3. 添加故障排查指南\n4. 更新 README\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n1. **镜像准备测试**\n   - 测试本地镜像推送\n   - 测试云端镜像验证\n   - 测试镜像 URL 构建\n\n2. **AgentCube 提供商测试**\n   - 测试 CR 创建\n   - 测试参数验证\n   - 测试错误处理\n\n3. **K8s 提供商测试**\n   - 测试 Deployment 创建\n   - 测试 Service 创建\n   - 测试等待就绪逻辑\n\n4. **错误处理测试**\n   - 测试输入验证\n   - 测试错误信息输出\n   - 测试日志记录\n\n### Integration Tests\n\n1. **Docker 集成测试**\n   - 测试真实镜像推送\n   - 测试凭证认证\n   - 测试镜像标记\n\n2. **Kubernetes 集成测试**\n   - 测试真实 K8s 部署\n   - 测试 AgentRuntime CR\n   - 测试标准 K8s 资源\n\n3. **完整流程测试**\n   - 测试 `pack` → `build` → `publish` 链路\n   - 测试 `publish` → `invoke` 链路\n   - 测试完整生命周期\n\n### Test Coverage\n\n目标：> 80% 代码覆盖率\n\n## Configuration\n\n### 命令行参数\n\n| 参数 | 类型 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n|------|------|--------|------|\n| `--workspace` / `-f` | str | `\".\"` | 工作空间路径 |\n| `--version` | str | `None` | 语义化版本号 |\n| `--image-url` | str | `None` | 镜像仓库 URL |\n| `--image-username` | str | `None` | 镜像仓库用户名 |\n| `--image-password` | str | `None` | 镜像仓库密码 |\n| `--description` | str | `None` | 代理描述 |\n| `--region` | str | `None` | 部署区域 |\n| `--cloud-provider` | str | `None` | 云服务提供商 |\n| `--provider` | str | `\"agentcube\"` | 目标提供商 |\n| `--node-port` | int | `None` | 节点端口 (30000-32767) |\n| `--replicas` | int | `None` | 副本数 |\n| `--namespace` | str | `None` | 命名空间 |\n| `--verbose` | bool | `False` | 详细日志 |\n\n### 元数据配置\n\n在 `agent_metadata.yaml` 中：\n\n```yaml\nagent_name: \"my-agent\"\nversion: \"1.0.0\"\ndescription: \"My AI agent\"\nlanguage: \"python\"\nentrypoint: \"python main.py\"\nport: 8080\nbuild_mode: \"local\"  # 或 \"cloud\"\n\n# 镜像配置\nimage:\n  name: \"my-agent\"\n  tag: \"1.0.0\"\n\n# 注册表配置（本地构建模式）\nregistry_url: \"registry.example.com\"\nregistry_username: \"admin\"\nregistry_password: \"secret\"\n\n# AgentCube 提供商配置\nrouter_url: \"http://router.agentcube.svc.cluster.local:8080\"\nworkload_manager_url: \"http://workload-manager.agentcube.svc.cluster.local:8080\"\nreadiness_probe_path: \"/health\"\nreadiness_probe_port: 8080\n\n# 部署信息（由 publish 命令更新）\nk8s_deployment:\n  type: \"AgentRuntime\"\n  namespace: \"default\"\n  agent_id: \"my-agent-abc123\"\n  agent_endpoint: \"http://my-agent.default.svc.cluster.local:8080\"\n  status: \"deployed\"\n```\n\n### 环境变量\n\n| 变量 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| `KUBECONFIG` | Kubernetes 配置文件路径 |\n| `DOCKER_HOST` | Docker 守护进程地址 |\n| `HTTP_PROXY` | HTTP 代理 |\n| `HTTPS_PROXY` | HTTPS 代理 |\n| `NO_PROXY` | 不使用代理的主机 |\n\n## API Specification\n\n### publish() 方法签名\n\n```python\ndef publish(\n    workspace_path: Path,\n    version: Optional[str] = None,\n    image_url: Optional[str] = None,\n    image_username: Optional[str] = None,\n    image_password: Optional[str] = None,\n    description: Optional[str] = None,\n    region: Optional[str] = None,\n    cloud_provider: Optional[str] = None,\n    provider: str = \"agentcube\",\n    node_port: Optional[int] = None,\n    replicas: Optional[int] = None,\n    namespace: Optional[str] = None,\n    verbose: bool = False\n) -> Dict[str, Any]\n```\n\n### 返回值\n\n**AgentCube 提供商**：\n```python\n{\n    \"agent_id\": \"my-agent-abc123\",\n    \"agent_endpoint\": \"http://my-agent.default.svc.cluster.local:8080\",\n    \"namespace\": \"default\",\n    \"agent_name\": \"my-agent\"\n}\n```\n\n**K8s 提供商**：\n```python\n{\n    \"deployment_name\": \"my-agent\",\n    \"service_name\": \"my-agent\",\n    \"namespace\": \"default\",\n    \"replicas\": 1,\n    \"container_port\": 8080,\n    \"node_port\": 30080,\n    \"service_url\": \"http://localhost:30080\",\n    \"agent_name\": \"my-agent\"\n}\n```\n\n### 异常\n\n- `ValueError` - 无效的输入参数\n- `RuntimeError` - Docker 不可用或部署失败\n- `TimeoutError` - 部署超时\n- `Exception` - 其他发布错误\n\n## Security Considerations\n\n1. **镜像凭证安全**\n   - 支持安全的镜像注册表认证（HTTPS）\n   - 避免在日志中输出凭证\n   - 支持凭证轮换\n\n2. **Kubernetes 访问安全**\n   - 验证 kubeconfig 配置\n   - 支持命名空间隔离\n   - 遵循最小权限原则\n\n3. **元数据安全**\n   - 避免在元数据中存储敏感信息\n   - 确保文件权限正确\n   - 支持元数据加密（可选）\n\n4. **部署安全**\n   - 验证镜像来源\n   - 支持镜像签名验证（可选）\n   - 限制资源使用\n\n## Performance Considerations\n\n1. **镜像推送性能**\n   - 支持镜像层缓存\n   - 支持并行推送（可选）\n   - 优化网络传输\n\n2. **部署性能**\n   - 利用 K8s 滚动更新\n   - 支持并行资源创建\n   - 优化健康检查\n\n3. **资源使用**\n   - 控制并发部署数\n   - 支持资源限制\n   - 优化内存使用\n\n## Monitoring and Metrics\n\n### 日志记录\n\n使用 Python 标准库 `logging`：\n\n- 发布开始/结束\n- 镜像准备进度\n- 部署状态\n- 错误信息\n- 调试信息（verbose 模式）\n\n### 发布指标\n\n- 发布时间\n- 镜像推送时间\n- 部署就绪时间\n- 发布成功率\n- 发布失败原因\n\n## Open Questions\n\n1. **Q1**: 是否需要支持多集群部署？\n   - **当前**: 不支持\n   - **讨论**: 支持同时部署到多个集群\n   - **决策**: 初始不支持，后续根据需求添加\n\n2. **Q2**: 是否需要支持金丝雀发布？\n   - **当前**: 不支持\n   - **讨论**: 支持金丝雀和蓝绿部署\n   - **决策**: 初始不支持，后续根据需求添加\n\n3. **Q3**: 是否需要支持自定义健康检查？\n   - **当前**: 使用默认健康检查\n   - **讨论**: 支持自定义健康检查配置\n   - **决策**: 初始使用默认配置，后续扩展\n\n4. **Q4**: 是否需要支持部署回滚？\n   - **当前**: 不支持\n   - **讨论**: 支持自动回滚和手动回滚\n   - **决策**: 初始不支持，后续根据需求添加\n\n## Next Steps\n\n1. 创建 PublishRuntime 类\n2. 实现镜像准备功能\n3. 实现 AgentCube 提供商\n4. 实现 K8s 提供商\n5. 实现 CLI 命令集成\n6. 编写单元测试和集成测试\n7. 更新文档\n8. 集成到 CI/CD 流程\n\n## References\n\n- [AgentCube CLI Design](../cli-toolkit/design.md)\n- [AgentCube CLI Spec](../cli-toolkit/spec.md)\n- [Kubernetes Python Client](https://github.com/kubernetes-client/python)\n- [Docker SDK for Python](https://docker-py.readthedocs.io/)\n- [Typer Documentation](https://typer.tiangolo.com/)","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775867461977,"end":1775867462258}}}}
